&lt;p&gt;Dioptas is an awesome GUI program based on &lt;em&gt;Python&lt;/em&gt;, designed for the fast data reduction of &lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Powder X-ray Diffraction images&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;. It provides the capability of &lt;strong&gt;calibrating&lt;/strong&gt;, &lt;strong&gt;integrating&lt;/strong&gt;, &lt;strong&gt;creating masks&lt;/strong&gt;, showing multiple pattern overlays and display phases line positions.&lt;/p&gt;</summary>
    
    
    
